<p>ChatGPT by OpenAI remains a highly versatile AI writing tool available. Powered by GPT-4o, it handles everything from blog posts and emails to code, creative writing, and brainstorming. Its strong free tier, extensive plugin ecosystem, and multimodal capabilities (image analysis, voice, data analysis) make it a well-rounded choice for most users. The new memory feature allows ChatGPT to learn your preferences and writing style over time.</p>

<h3>Test Results</h3>
<p><strong>Prompt used:</strong> "Write a 500-word blog post about the benefits of remote work for productivity, including statistics and actionable tips"</p>
<ul>
<li>Writing quality: 9.5/10 — natural, engaging prose with excellent structure</li>
<li>Generation time: ~4 seconds</li>
<li>Factual accuracy: 9/10 — correctly cited recent remote work statistics</li>
<li>Tone flexibility: 9.5/10 — adapted perfectly to professional, casual, and persuasive tones</li>
<li>SEO optimization: 8.5/10 — good keyword placement and heading structure</li>
</ul>

